mmit", "elapsed_ms": 76.9, "extra": {"branch": "agent", "skip_polish": true}}, {"stage": "ask_customer_service.total", "elapsed_ms": 7201.9, "extra": {"branch": "agent", "intent": "recommend_products", "agent_mode": "llm_tool_calling"}}, {"stage": "ask_stream.service_call", "elapsed_ms": 7206.93, "extra": {"conversation_id": "7a266d45-dafa-4837-ae6c-15f6e0a98315", "intent": "recommend_products", "agent_mode": "llm_tool_calling"}}, {"stage": "ask_stream.total", "elapsed_ms": 7258.14, "extra": {"conversation_id": "7a266d45-dafa-4837-ae6c-15f6e0a98315", "intent": "recommend_products"}}], "first_answer_delta_ms": 6450.13, "done_ms": 7256.76, "final_answer": "根据2人露营做饭的需求，我推荐爱路客的露营套锅（CW-C01-37）。这款锅专为1-2人设计，容量组合为900ml锅+450ml碗，足够两人简单烹饪。它重量仅595g，非常轻便，采用硬质氧化铝合金材质，耐用且导热快。最大的亮点是全包围防风底座，火力更稳定，且支持燃气和酒精两种燃料，适合不同场景。整体可叠加收纳，节省背包空间，价格定位中端，性价比很高。", "intent": "recommend_products", "agent_mode": "llm_tool_calling"}}
